class TestFrequency{
	public int getFrequency(String[] article,int n,String word){
		int sum = 0;
		if(n <= 1000){
			for(int i = 0;i < n;i++){
				if(article[i].equals(word)){
					sum++;
				}
			}
		}
		
		return sum;
	}
